  "raw_html": "<button type='button' role='link' class='btn btn-link p-0 text-start' id='link_3' aria-label=\" Gauri Mahto @ Gauri Kumar versus The State of Bihar pdf\"  class='noToken' href='#' onclick=javascript:open_pdf('3','2025','2025_2_2122_2129','2025INSC817'); ><font size='4'> <strong>GAURI MAHTO @ GAURI KUMAR<span class='fst-italic'> versus </span>THE STATE OF BIHAR </strong>- <span class='escrText'>[2025] 2 S.C.R. 2122</span><span class='ncDisplay'>2025 INSC 817</span><input type='hidden' id='cnr' value=ESCR010007242025></button></font><br><strong>Coram : J.K. MAHESHWARI<sup style=\"color: #268e97;font-size: 22px;top: 0;\" class=\"tooltip-sup\" data-tooltip=\"Author\">*</sup>, ARAVIND KUMAR</strong><br> Issue for Consideration Whether in the facts of the case, prima-facie offence u/s.364-A, IPC against appellant is made out or not. Headnotes&dagger; Penal Code, 1860 &ndash; s.364-A &ndash; Kidnapping for ransom, etc. &ndash; Offence u/s.364-A, if prima-facie made out against appellant: Held: No whether the house from where the child (PW-12) was recovered belonged to appellant or not &ndash; Appellant was not identified either by the father (PW-13) of the child or the child himself &ndash; No cogent evidence regarding any ransom demand made by the appellant &ndash; Furthermore, the<br><strong class='caseDetailsTD' ><span style='color:#212F3D' > Decision Date :</span><font color='green'> 27-02-2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Case No :</span><font color='green'> CRIMINAL APPEAL No. 1134/2016</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Disposal Nature :</span><font color='green'> Appeal(s) allowed</font>   <span style='color:#212F3D' > |  Bench :</span><font color='green'> 2 Judges</font></strong><div class='row my-1 mt-2 border bg-light'><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('3','2025','2025_2_2122_2129','2025INSC817','S')><i <i class='fas fa-columns me-2'></i>Split view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('3','2025','2025_2_2122_2129','2025INSC817','H'); ><i class='fas fa-file-alt me-2'></i>HTML view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_flip('3','2025','2025_2_2122_2129','2025INSC817');><i class='fas fa-book-open me-2' ></i>Flip view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_pdf('3','2025','2025_2_2122_2129','2025INSC817','N'); ><i class='fas fa-file-pdf me-2'></i>PDF</a></div></div>",
